|2 |  RECURSIVE UNION ALL|    |
|3 |   SORT              |    |
|4 |    TABLE SCAN       |e   |
|5 |   HASH JOIN         |    |
|6 |    TABLE SCAN       |e   |
|7 |    TABLE SCAN       |r   |
===============================

